Class AbstractListTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • testDatastructures.AbstractListTest
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CircularLinkedListTest

    public abstract class AbstractListTest
extends java.lang.Object
    Tests the AbstractList class. An empty list should be passed to make sure that the tests pass.
